### the findings (phase 2 audit)

```
1. BFPT (#36) is EXTERNAL
   - Proven by Shamrock-Frost, but not in Mathlib core.
   - We cannot import it without a full port.

2. Homotopy Groups (π_n) are SKELETON
   - Type definitions exist (HomotopyGroup.Pi).
   - Computations (π_n(Sⁿ) = ℤ) are marked TODO.
   - No-retraction theorem is not derivable without them.

3. Result
   - We must build the tools to build the bridge.
```

[proof strategy details](research/hero_scenarios/broken_bridge/invariance_of_domain/proof_strategy.三語)

